{{message|A gush of water hits <monster> on the <body part>!|A monster's armor in the corresponding slot takes water damage.}}
{{message|<monster> falls to pieces!|An iron golem was hit by the trap and died.}}
{{message|May <monster> rust in peace.|[[YAFM|As above, but the iron golem was tame and was out of sight.]]}}

== Variants ==
In [[SLASH'EM]] and [[dNetHack]], untrapping a rust trap will turn the trap into a [[fountain]] if successful.

